@redtact/deepslate-extras (part of structure-viewer)
Copyright 2026 redtact

This package includes software derived from deepslate
(https://github.com/misode/deepslate) by Misode, which is licensed under
the MIT License.

Specifically:

- FadeRenderer.ts: the GLSL vertex/fragment shaders are modified copies
  of deepslate's standard block and line shaders.
- deepslatePatches.ts: contains optimized derived copies of
  implementation from the deepslate distribution (Mesh.prototype.rebuild
  / merge / clear / isEmpty / quadVertices / quadIndices and
  Renderer.prototype.setVertexAttr / setUniform / prepareDraw /
  drawMesh), applied as runtime prototype patches that preserve the
  original output bit-for-bit.

